0.08     2014-07-24 (SHARYANTO)

         - Adjust to Getopt::Long::Util 0.46 (required by
           Perinci::Sub::GetArgs::Argv 0.46) which already sorts options.

         [BUG FIXES]

         - Don't add newline if result is an empty string.

